--- Part 5: Why certain intersection graphs are impossible ---
  Checking: do intersecting 3-cycles always splice to create more?
    bits=10: [0, 1, 2] ∩ [0, 3, 4] = [0] → splice creates 5-cycle on [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]
